# Documentation Sync on Infrastructure Change

When infrastructure behavior changes, documentation must be updated in the same work session.

## Required updates

- Update runbooks such as `Runpod_VM.md` when pod specs, image/template, ports, startup commands, or deployment wiring change.
- Update environment variable guidance in README or runbooks when endpoint contracts change.
- Record newly observed operational failure signatures and resolutions in troubleshooting sections.

## Completion rule

Do not consider infrastructure work complete until documentation reflects the latest known-good working state.
